For this blockchain introduction assignment: 
- Create a detailed report explaining the fundamental concepts of blockchain 
- Compare at least 3 different blockchain platforms (Ethereum, Solana, etc.) 
- Explain the differences between proof-of-work and proof-of-stake - Set up a local blockchain environment (e.g., Ganache)
- Create a simple transaction on a test network - Include screenshots of your local blockchain and transactions
- Reflect on potential use cases for blockchain technology

